picture><source srcSet=\"/static/51bc6cff28ea890057a746d095670e02/593c8/image004-Fran-Yanity.jpg 53w,\n/static/51bc6cff28ea890057a746d095670e02/c9baa/image004-Fran-Yanity.jpg 107w,\n/static/51bc6cff28ea890057a746d095670e02/6704b/image004-Fran-Yanity.jpg 213w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 213px) 100vw, 213px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 213px) 100vw, 213px\" srcSet=\"/static/51bc6cff28ea890057a746d095670e02/593c8/image004-Fran-Yanity.jpg 53w,\n/static/51bc6cff28ea890057a746d095670e02/c9baa/image004-Fran-Yanity.jpg 107w,\n/static/51bc6cff28ea890057a746d095670e02/6704b/image004-Fran-Yanity.jpg 213w\" src=\"/static/51bc6cff28ea890057a746d095670e02/6704b/image004-Fran-Yanity.jpg\" alt=\"Fran Yanity, President of The PM Group\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/51bc6cff28ea890057a746d095670e02/593c8/image004-Fran-Yanity.jpg 53w,\n/static/51bc6cff28ea890057a746d095670e02/c9baa/image004-Fran-Yanity.jpg 107w,\n/static/51bc6cff28ea890057a746d095670e02/6704b/image004-Fran-Yanity.jpg 213w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 213px) 100vw, 213px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 213px) 100vw, 213px\" srcset=\"/static/51bc6cff28ea890057a746d095670e02/593c8/image004-Fran-Yanity.jpg 53w,\n/static/51bc6cff28ea890057a746d095670e02/c9baa/image004-Fran-Yanity.jpg 107w,\n/static/51bc6cff28ea890057a746d095670e02/6704b/image004-Fran-Yanity.jpg 213w\" src=\"/static/51bc6cff28ea890057a746d095670e02/6704b/image004-Fran-Yanity.jpg\" alt=\"Fran Yanity, President of The PM Group\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span></p>\n<p>The PM Group, San Antonio’s largest advertising agency, recently announced the addition of <a href=\"https://thepmgrp.com/leadership-fran-yanity/\">Fran Yanity</a> to the agency’s executive leadership team. Ms. Yanity rejoins the agency as President/COO, a position she previously held until 2013.<br />\nWith experience on both the agency and client sides of the business, Ms. Yanity brings over 25 years of advertising, marketing, PR and promotions expertise to the agency. She joins Bob Wills, CEO, Debbie Tweedy, Executive Vice President and Rebecca Kassner, Controller, as part of the executive leadership team. Ms. Yanity will focus on agency operations, client satisfaction and retention, as well as new business initiatives.</p>\n","title":"The PM Group Announces New President/COO","seo":{"breadcrumbs":[{"text":"The PM Group Announces New President/COO","url":"/the-pm-group-announces-new-presidentcoo/"}],"title":"The PM Group Announce New President & COO | The PM Group","metaDesc":"The PM Group announces a new President and Chief Operations Officer, with experience on both agency and client sides of the business.","focuskw":"","metaKeywords":"","metaRobotsNoindex":"index","metaRobotsNofollow":"follow","opengraphTitle":"The PM Group Announce New President & COO | The PM Group","opengraphDescription":"The PM Group announces a new President and Chief Operations Officer, with experience on both agency and client sides of the business.","opengraphImage":null,"twitterTitle":"","twitterDescription":"","twitterImage":null,"canonical":"/the-pm-group-announces-new-presidentcoo/","cornerstone":false,"schema":{"raw":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@graph\":[{\"@type\":\"WebSite\",\"@id\":\"/#website\",\"url\":\"/\",\"name\":\"The PM Group\",\"description\":\"San Antonio\\u2019s Largest Advertising and Marketing Agency\",\"potentialAction\":[{\"@type\":\"SearchAction\",\"target\":{\"@type\":\"EntryPoint\",\"urlTemplate\":\"/?s={search_term_string}\"},\"query-input\":\"required name=search_term_string\"}],\"inLanguage\":\"en-US\"},{\"@type\":\"ImageObject\",\"@id\":\"/the-pm-group-announces-new-presidentcoo/#primaryimage\",\"inLanguage\":\"en-US\",\"url\":\"/static/e9dae4fb